    .container.top-spacings
        .row
            .col
                h5 About Us
                p
                    | A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia. It is a paradisematic
                    | country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth.
            .col(style='padding-left: 100px')
                h5(style='margin-left: 30px; padding-bottom: 25px') Navigation
                ul
                    li About
